I ⚡️💙 NEW YORK

🎥: @coltkirwan
move to nyc, they said…

2023, I’m grateful.

I’m grateful for a family that pushes me to see a world outside of America hahah. ありがとう、日本！

I’m grateful for the random morning texts to spontaneously ice bath.

I’m grateful to have found a love for running and gosh, even accept to run NYC’s 26.2.

I’m grateful for Producer @kenchwatek for helping me discover a new creative toolbox. 

I’m grateful for the serendipity this city offers.

I’m NOT grateful for developing a sprite and subway addiction this year hahaha, nor the friends that fueled this addiction. 😒

I’m grateful for these 3 hooligans, us 4 roll as 1.

I’m grateful for the Content Closet. A warped, dusty, cluttered apartment I despised at first but now, I can’t imagine going anywhere else.

And of course, I’m grateful for the ability to wake up in this incredible city. It changed the way I look at life.

2024… the drive, the ideas, the excitement I have right now is unlike any other. Let’s tango.
